  "text": "We’re renovating a farmhouse about an hour outside New York City and I’m so excited to be able to host friends there. I think I’m actually more excited about the guest rooms than any of the other spaces. The bedrooms won’t need any more renovations (the kitchen and bathrooms are still being worked on) so I’ve slowly started putting the rooms together. We’ve partnered with Purple to share our tips for putting together a guest bedroom. Let us know what you’d add to the list. 1. Add a luggage rack to make it feel like you’re a professional host. 2. Make the bed with a comfy mattress and pillow from Purple! Side Note: Get 10% off your Purple orders with code OHD10 now through November 4, 2021. 3. Put water on bedside table and a chocolate on pillow so it feels like turndown service at a fancy hotel. 4. Steal a sprig from the yard to a touch of wild. 5. Add a card with WiFi and information about stay. It’s always so nice when you don’t have to ask. 6. Pick out books the guest would like from your library and leave in the room. 7. Always sleep in the guest room at least once to give it a dry run. You’ll notice if it gets cold, or you need blackout shades, etc. This post is sponsored by Purple. Styling and photography by Kate Jordan for Oh Happy Day.",
  "image": "",
  "html": "\u003cdiv id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003carticle id=\"post-64776\" role=\"article\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"http://schema.org/BlogPosting\"\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003csection itemprop=\"articleBody\"\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\u003cp\u003eWe’re renovating a farmhouse about an hour outside New York City and I’m so excited to be able to host friends there. I think I’m actually more excited about the guest rooms than any of the other spaces. The bedrooms won’t need any more renovations (the kitchen and bathrooms are still being worked on) so I’ve slowly started putting the rooms together.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://d2c5oomqu2hs08.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/BLOG_20210718_KateJordan_JordanFerneyxPurple0024.jpg\"\u003e\u003cimg fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"600\" height=\"900\" src=\"https://d2c5oomqu2hs08.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/BLOG_20210718_KateJordan_JordanFerneyxPurple0024.jpg\" alt=\"7 Tips for Putting Together a Guest Room | Oh Happy Day\" srcset=\"https://d2c5oomqu2hs08.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/BLOG_20210718_KateJordan_JordanFerneyxPurple0024.jpg 600w, https://d2c5oomqu2hs08.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/BLOG_20210718_KateJordan_JordanFerneyxPurple0024-200x300.jpg 200w, https://d2c5oomqu2hs08.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/BLOG_20210718_KateJordan_JordanFerneyxPurple0024-16x24.jpg 16w, https://d2c5oomqu2hs08.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/BLOG_20210718_KateJordan_JordanFerneyxPurple0024-24x36.jpg 24w, https://d2c5oomqu2hs08.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/BLOG_20210718_KateJordan_JordanFerneyxPurple0024-32x48.jpg 32w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cspan id=\"more-64776\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eWe’ve partnered with \u003ca href=\"https://purple.com?utm_medium=rf\u0026amp;utm_source=ohd\u0026amp;utm_content=farmhouse\u0026amp;utm_campaign=mattress\u0026amp;utm_term=br\"\u003ePurple\u003c/a\u003e to share our tips for putting together a guest bedroom. Let us know what you’d add to the list.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003e1. Add a luggage rack to make it feel like you’re a professional host.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://d2c5oomqu2hs08.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/BLOG_20210718_KateJordan_JordanFerneyxPurple0023-1.jpg\"\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://d2c5oomqu2hs08.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/BLOG_20210718_KateJordan_JordanFerneyxPurple0023-1.jpg\" alt=\"7 Tips for Putting Together a Guest Room | Oh Happy Day\" width=\"600\" height=\"900\" srcset=\"https://d2c5oomqu2hs08.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/BLOG_20210718_KateJordan_JordanFerneyxPurple0023-1.jpg 600w, https://d2c5oomqu2hs08.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/BLOG_20210718_KateJordan_JordanFerneyxPurple0023-1-200x300.jpg 200w, https://d2c5oomqu2hs08.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/BLOG_20210718_KateJordan_JordanFerneyxPurple0023-1-16x24.jpg 16w, https://d2c5oomqu2hs08.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/BLOG_20210718_KateJordan_JordanFerneyxPurple0023-1-24x36.jpg 24w, https://d2c5oomqu2hs08.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/BLOG_20210718_KateJordan_JordanFerneyxPurple0023-1-32x48.jpg 32w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr/\u003e2. Make the bed with a comfy \u003ca href=\"https://purple.com/mattresses?utm_medium=rf\u0026amp;utm_source=ohd\u0026amp;utm_content=farmhouse\u0026amp;utm_campaign=mattress\u0026amp;utm_term=br\"\u003emattress\u003c/a\u003e and pillow from Purple! Side Note: Get 10% off your Purple orders with code \u003cstrong\u003e\u003cspan\u003eOHD10\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/strong\u003e now through November 4, 2021.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://d2c5oomqu2hs08.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/BLOG_20210718_KateJordan_JordanFerneyxPurple0029-1.jpg\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"600\" height=\"900\" src=\"https://d2c5oomqu2hs08.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/BLOG_20210718_KateJordan_JordanFerneyxPurple0029-1.jpg\" alt=\"7 Tips for Putting Together a Guest Room | Oh Happy Day\" srcset=\"https://d2c5oomqu2hs08.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/BLOG_20210718_KateJordan_JordanFerneyxPurple0029-1.jpg 600w, https://d2c5oomqu2hs08.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/BLOG_20210718_KateJordan_JordanFerneyxPurple0029-1-200x300.jpg 200w, https://d2c5oomqu2hs08.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/BLOG_20210718_KateJordan_JordanFerneyxPurple0029-1-16x24.jpg 16w, https://d2c5oomqu2hs08.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/BLOG_20210718_KateJordan_JordanFerneyxPurple0029-1-24x36.jpg 24w, https://d2c5oomqu2hs08.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/BLOG_20210718_KateJordan_JordanFerneyxPurple0029-1-32x48.jpg 32w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr/\u003e3. Put water on bedside table and a chocolate on pillow so it feels like turndown service at a fancy hotel.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://d2c5oomqu2hs08.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/BLOG_20210718_KateJordan_JordanFerneyxPurple0043.jpg\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"600\" height=\"900\" src=\"https://d2c5oomqu2hs08.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/BLOG_20210718_KateJordan_JordanFerneyxPurple0043.jpg\" alt=\"7 Tips for Putting Together a Guest Room | Oh Happy Day\" srcset=\"https://d2c5oomqu2hs08.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/BLOG_20210718_KateJordan_JordanFerneyxPurple0043.jpg 600w, https://d2c5oomqu2hs08.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/BLOG_20210718_KateJordan_JordanFerneyxPurple0043-200x300.jpg 200w, https://d2c5oomqu2hs08.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/BLOG_20210718_KateJordan_JordanFerneyxPurple0043-16x24.jpg 16w, https://d2c5oomqu2hs08.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/BLOG_20210718_KateJordan_JordanFerneyxPurple0043-24x36.jpg 24w, https://d2c5oomqu2hs08.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/BLOG_20210718_KateJordan_JordanFerneyxPurple0043-32x48.jpg 32w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr/\u003e4. Steal a sprig from the yard to a touch of wild.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://d2c5oomqu2hs08.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/BLOG_20210718_KateJordan_JordanFerneyxPurple0003-1.jpg\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"600\" height=\"900\" src=\"https://d2c5oomqu2hs08.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/BLOG_20210718_KateJordan_JordanFerneyxPurple0003-1.jpg\" alt=\"7 Tips for Putting Together a Guest Room | Oh Happy Day\" srcset=\"https://d2c5oomqu2hs08.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/BLOG_20210718_KateJordan_JordanFerneyxPurple0003-1.jpg 600w, https://d2c5oomqu2hs08.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/BLOG_20210718_KateJordan_JordanFerneyxPurple0003-1-200x300.jpg 200w, https://d2c5oomqu2hs08.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/BLOG_20210718_KateJordan_JordanFerneyxPurple0003-1-16x24.jpg 16w, https://d2c5oomqu2hs08.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/BLOG_20210718_KateJordan_JordanFerneyxPurple0003-1-24x36.jpg 24w, https://d2c5oomqu2hs08.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/BLOG_20210718_KateJordan_JordanFerneyxPurple0003-1-32x48.jpg 32w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr/\u003e5. Add a card with WiFi and information about stay. It’s always so nice when you don’t have to ask.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://d2c5oomqu2hs08.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/BLOG_20210718_KateJordan_JordanFerneyxPurple0010.jpg\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"600\" height=\"900\" src=\"https://d2c5oomqu2hs08.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/BLOG_20210718_KateJordan_JordanFerneyxPurple0010.jpg\" alt=\"7 Tips for Putting Together a Guest Room | Oh Happy Day\" srcset=\"https://d2c5oomqu2hs08.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/BLOG_20210718_KateJordan_JordanFerneyxPurple0010.jpg 600w, https://d2c5oomqu2hs08.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/BLOG_20210718_KateJordan_JordanFerneyxPurple0010-200x300.jpg 200w, https://d2c5oomqu2hs08.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/BLOG_20210718_KateJordan_JordanFerneyxPurple0010-16x24.jpg 16w, https://d2c5oomqu2hs08.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/BLOG_20210718_KateJordan_JordanFerneyxPurple0010-24x36.jpg 24w, https://d2c5oomqu2hs08.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/BLOG_20210718_KateJordan_JordanFerneyxPurple0010-32x48.jpg 32w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr/\u003e6. Pick out books the guest would like from your library and leave in the room.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://d2c5oomqu2hs08.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/BLOG_20210718_KateJordan_JordanFerneyxPurple0060.jpg\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"600\" height=\"900\" src=\"https://d2c5oomqu2hs08.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/BLOG_20210718_KateJordan_JordanFerneyxPurple0060.jpg\" alt=\"7 Tips for Putting Together a Guest Room | Oh Happy Day\" srcset=\"https://d2c5oomqu2hs08.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/BLOG_20210718_KateJordan_JordanFerneyxPurple0060.jpg 600w, https://d2c5oomqu2hs08.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/BLOG_20210718_KateJordan_JordanFerneyxPurple0060-200x300.jpg 200w, https://d2c5oomqu2hs08.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/BLOG_20210718_KateJordan_JordanFerneyxPurple0060-16x24.jpg 16w, https://d2c5oomqu2hs08.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/BLOG_20210718_KateJordan_JordanFerneyxPurple0060-24x36.jpg 24w, https://d2c5oomqu2hs08.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/BLOG_20210718_KateJordan_JordanFerneyxPurple0060-32x48.jpg 32w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr/\u003e7. Always sleep in the guest room at least once to give it a dry run. You’ll notice if it gets cold, or you need blackout shades, etc.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr/\u003e\u003cem\u003eThis post is sponsored by Purple. \u003c/em\u003e\u003cbr/\u003e\u003cem\u003eStyling and photography by Kate Jordan for Oh Happy Day.\u003c/em\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003c/section\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003c/article\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e",
